title: Try Not To Laugh #78 - Shayne's Birthday!
author: Smosh Pit
description:
It's not Monday, but it is Shayne's birthday so today's Try Not To Laugh challenge is a toast to some of Shayne's best bits ever! 

This video was shot with a very limited crew. All cast & crew followed all CDC and California COVID-19 precautions and filming guidelines.

Punch that bell icon so you'll know when we add a new episode!
